  "customHelp": "How to setup this game:\n (1.) At start draw 5 cards from your main deck. You can make a mulligan: put all cards from your hand to bottom main deck, then draw a new hand (5 cards).\n (2.) Click and hold the top card of your main deck, drag it to shields deck, repeat this process 6 times. After this, you should have 6 cards in your shield \"deck\", shuffle then. \n(3.) Create a EX-BASE token. \n(4.) If you play first, draw one resource card from your resources deck and draw 1 card. If you play at last, create a EX Resource token. That's it.",
